# KabuTech Firebase Migration — Complete Plan

## Goal

Move **everything that needs shared/persistent data** from localStorage to Firebase, so the app works across devices and supports real multi-user collaboration.

---

## Complete Feature Audit

### 🔐 1. Authentication & User Accounts

| Feature | Current (localStorage) | Firebase Target |
|---|---|---|
| Login | `kb_user` — session stored locally | Firebase Auth `signInWithEmailAndPassword()` |
| Register | `kb_accounts` — plaintext passwords! | Firebase Auth `createUserWithEmailAndPassword()` |
| Logout | `localStorage.removeItem('kb_user')` | `firebase.auth().signOut()` |
| Auto-login on refresh | Reads `kb_user` | `onAuthStateChanged()` listener |
| Remember me | localStorage persistence | Firebase Auth session persistence |

**Functions to change:** `handleLogin()` [L2055](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L2055), `handleRegister()` [L1969](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L1969), `handleLogout()` [L2199](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L2199), `getAccounts()` [L2016](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L2016), `saveAccounts()` [L2020](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L2020)

---

### 👥 2. Staff Account Management (Admin CRUD)

This is critical — admin needs to **create, read, update, and delete** staff accounts.

| Feature | Current | Firebase Target |
|---|---|---|
| List staff accounts | `getAccounts().filter(role !== 'admin')` | Read from `/kabutech/users` collection |
| Create staff | Push to `kb_accounts` array | Firebase Auth `createUser()` + write profile to `/kabutech/users/{uid}` |
| Edit staff (name, password) | Direct array mutation | Update Auth profile + update `/kabutech/users/{uid}` |
| Delete staff | Filter out of array | Firebase Auth delete user + remove from `/kabutech/users/{uid}` |
| Search staff | Client-side filter | Client-side filter on cached `/kabutech/users` data |

**Functions to change:** `renderStaffAccountsList()` [L5052](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L5052), `renderStaffDirectoryDesktop()` [L5096](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L5096), `openStaffAccountModal()` [L5180](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L5180), `saveStaffAccount()` [L5230](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L5230), `confirmDeleteStaff()` [L5288](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L5288)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Admin creating/deleting other users' Firebase Auth accounts requires a Cloud Function.** Firebase client SDK can only manage the currently signed-in user. We'll use a simple Cloud Function that the admin calls to create/delete staff auth accounts.

**Alternative (simpler):** Admin creates staff profiles in the database only. Staff self-registers through the signup page, and admin "approves" them by linking the profile. This avoids needing Cloud Functions.

