### 🌱 3. Grow Batches (Racks + Bags)

| Feature | Current | Firebase Target |
|---|---|---|
| All rack data | `kb_batches` array | `/kabutech/batches/{batchId}` |
| Add rack | Push to array → `saveBatches()` | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/batches').push(newRack)` |
| Edit rack | Mutate array → `saveBatches()` | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/batches/' + id).update(...)` |
| Delete rack | Filter array → `saveBatches()` | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/batches/' + id).remove()` |
| Save function | `saveBatches()` [L739](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L739) | Write to RTDB |
| Load function | `localStorage.getItem('kb_batches')` [L653](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L653) | `onValue()` listener |

---

### 🫑 4. Harvest Logs (Inside Bags)

| Feature | Current | Firebase Target |
|---|---|---|
| Log harvest per bag | Push `{date, grams}` to `bag.harvestLog[]` | Same — nested inside batch data in RTDB |
| Bulk harvest | Iterate selected bags → push to each | Same — batch update then `saveBatches()` → RTDB |
| Replant (clear harvest) | Reset `bag.harvestLog = []` | Same structure, writes to RTDB |
| Yield calculation | Sum all `harvestLog.grams` across batches | Same client-side calc, data from RTDB |

**Functions to change:** `openBagHarvestModal()` [L4222](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L4222), `_confirmBulkHarvest()` [L5368](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L5368), `replantBag()` [L4070](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L4070), `removeBagSlot()` [L4132](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js#L4132)

> [!TIP]
> Harvest data is nested inside batches (`batches[].bags[].harvestLog[]`), so it migrates automatically when we migrate batches to Firebase. No separate collection needed.

