## Proposed Changes

### [NEW] [js/firebase-config.js](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/firebase-config.js)

Core Firebase module:
- Firebase init with user's config keys
- `onAuthStateChanged()` — auto-login, session persistence
- `onValue()` listeners for all 8 data collections
- Write helper functions (`fbSaveBatches()`, `fbSaveTasks()`, etc.)
- Connection status monitor (online/offline badge)
- Staff account CRUD functions (create via Auth, profile via RTDB)

### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/index.html)

- Add 3 Firebase SDK `<script>` tags before `</head>`
- Add `<script src="./js/firebase-config.js">` after `app.js`

### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///home/zandro/Documents/KabuTech%20App%20v4/js/app.js)

**8 save functions** → replace localStorage writes with Firebase writes:

| Function | Line | Change to |
|---|---|---|
| `saveBatches()` | L739 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/batches').set(state.growBatches)` |
| `saveTasks()` | L740 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/tasks').set(state.tasks)` |
| `saveLogs()` | L741 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/logs').set(state.eventLogs)` |
| `saveAlerts()` | L742 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/alerts').set(state.alerts)` |
| `saveStaffReports()` | L743 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/staffReports').set(state.staffReports)` |
| `saveYieldTarget()` | L744 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/settings/yieldTarget').set(...)` |
| `saveSetpoints()` | L747 | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/settings/setpoints').set(...)` |
| `saveScheduleConfig()` | L797+ | `fbDB.ref('kabutech/settings/schedule').set(...)` |

**Auth functions** → replace localStorage auth with Firebase Auth:

| Function | Change |
|---|---|
| `handleLogin()` | `fbAuth.signInWithEmailAndPassword()` |
| `handleRegister()` | `fbAuth.createUserWithEmailAndPassword()` |
| `handleLogout()` | `fbAuth.signOut()` |
| `getAccounts()` | Read from cached `/kabutech/users` |
| `saveAccounts()` | Write to `/kabutech/users` |

**Staff CRUD** → use Firebase Auth + RTDB user profiles:

| Function | Change |
|---|---|
| `saveStaffAccount()` (create) | `fbAuth.createUserWithEmailAndPassword()` + write profile to `/kabutech/users/{uid}` |
| `saveStaffAccount()` (edit) | Update `/kabutech/users/{uid}` (name change). Password change via Auth admin |
| `confirmDeleteStaff()` | Remove from `/kabutech/users/{uid}`. Auth deletion via admin function |
| `renderStaffAccountsList()` | Read from cached users array (synced via `onValue`) |

**Init/load** → remove all `localStorage.getItem('kb_*')` for data (keep zoom/onboarding):

Data now arrives via `onValue()` listeners set up in `firebase-config.js`.

