## What You Need to Do (~10 min)

1. Create Firebase project at [console.firebase.google.com](https://console.firebase.google.com) → name it `kabutech-hiyas`
2. Enable **Email/Password** auth → Build → Authentication → Get Started → Enable
3. Create **Realtime Database** → Build → Realtime Database → Create → Singapore → Test mode
4. Register web app → Project Settings → `</>` → Copy `firebaseConfig` → **Paste to me**
5. Create 2 test users in Auth → Users → Add User:
   - `admin@kabutech.com` / `kabutech2026`
   - `staff@kabutech.com` / `kabutech2026`

