## Verification Plan

| Test | How |
|---|---|
| Login with Firebase Auth | Open app → login → check Firebase Console Auth logs |
| Data persistence | Create a batch → refresh page → batch still there |
| Multi-device sync | Login on phone + desktop → create task on one → appears on other |
| Staff CRUD | Admin creates staff → staff can login → admin edits → admin deletes |
| Harvest logging | Open rack → tap bag → log harvest → check batch data in Firebase |
| Offline fallback | Disconnect internet → app shows last data + "Offline" badge |
| Role restrictions | Login as staff → verify admin-only sections hidden |
